# Vercel (collarone.vercel.app) is a FALLBACK — production is the VPS
# (collarone.app), where server/index.js mounts every api/*.js via Express with
# no function cap. Vercel's Hobby plan caps at 12 serverless functions, so we
# keep the Vercel bundle under that ceiling here.
#
# paystack-webhook.js is server-to-server only: Paystack calls it at the fixed
# collarone.app URL, never the browser and never Vercel. Excluding it from the
# fallback loses no user-facing feature and keeps us at 12 functions. The VPS
# still gets it (rsync in deploy/deploy.sh doesn't read this file).
api/paystack-webhook.js
